{"tid":762432,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[代po]［尋人］[黃子華金盆𠺘口]","createTime":"2018-07-31T09:27:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-31T10:43:44.000Z","uid":29842,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f0ba304f62982953e2b0a039fa8b18285952eaa8","tid":762432,"uid":29842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T09:27:12.000Z","msg":"事緣30/7我去左紅館搏子華神嘅飛，8:15開場，我6:30到咗，問咗好多人最平都$1600張，喺我感到無助嘅時候，有人主動走埋黎，第一下都驚係保安，點知原來大家都係求飛，咁大家就識左，一齊行，當邊行邊問價問到8:00，我都冇太大既期望，因為仲炒緊$1800，好好奇點解愈炒愈貴。<br />\n<br />\n去到8:20放棄啦，打算走嘅時候，見到有個女人畀班黃牛圍住，我地過去了解下啦，點知個女人入唔到場，黃牛叫佢放飛比佢，點知啱啱識既朋友就講：「唔好放比黃牛，放比我個朋友，一張夠啦，我唔睇，我地係真&middot;FANS，我唔係黃牛，我可以唔睇，但求下你放畀我個朋友。」<br />\n<br />\n點知個女人真係放畀我，可惜最後都入唔到場，但我真係好感動，係呢個一票難求，畀班仆街黃牛搶哂飛嘅世界，竟然會仲有人肯去讓張飛比我，我真係好多謝佢🙇&zwj;♂🙇&zwj;♂🙇&zwj;♂"},{"pid":"d48ad5ed9c606b3c1fa5bb4f4e6215edef325938","tid":762432,"uid":12035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T09:30:44.000Z","msg":"點解最後係入唔到場"},{"pid":"0cdf4da1da077ab6e17be8a43658058d762a1646","tid":762432,"uid":187181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T09:33:45.000Z","msg":"放俾你但你入唔到場, 唔係代表佢搵你笨咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c49a97771c1bd8bb0a2738817ce523051542129","tid":762432,"uid":186372,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T09:43:58.000Z","msg":"是咪佢<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/31/174309_0d25abbd806a1a5fa72f42e90eef0d25.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F31%2F174309_0d25abbd806a1a5fa72f42e90eef0d25.png&h=faa42829&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bafa5fc29dfd3e26ac133dfb82350ecc4e2a4109","tid":762432,"uid":29842,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1c49a97771c1bd8bb0a2738817ce523051542129","tid":762432,"uid":186372,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T09:43:58.000Z","msg":"是咪佢<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/31/174309_0d25abbd806a1a5fa72f42e90eef0d25.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F31%2F174309_0d25abbd806a1a5fa72f42e90eef0d25.png&h=faa42829&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T10:43:44.000Z","msg":"係佢，我個朋友同佢相認了，thanks 巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}